<BR CLEAR=ALL> 

<P> Football star Marcus Allen recounts his jailhouse conversations 

with O.J. Simpson and denies that he had a romantic relationship with 

Nicole Brown Simpson in this May, 31 1996 deposition.</P> 

<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT> 

<PRE> 

 

Marcus Lamarr Allen - 5/31/96 

 

SUPERIOR COURT of THE STATE OF CALIFORNIA 

 

FOR THE COUNTY OF LOS ANGELES 

SHARON RUFO, ) 

 

Plaintiff, ) 

 

vs. 

ORENTHAL JAME3 SIMPSON et al.) 

 

Defendant. 

FREDRIC GOLDMAN, etc. et al.,) Case No. SC 031947 

Plaintiffs,) Case No. SC 036340 

And 

vs. Case No. SC 036876 

 

ORENTHAL JAMES SIMPSON, et al.,) 

 

Defendants. 

LOUIS H. BROWN, etc.) 

Plaintiffs 

vs.  

ORENTHAL JAMES SIMPSON, Defendant.) 

 

VIDEOTAPED DEPOSITION or: MARCUS LAMARR ALLEN 

DATE TAKEN: May 31, 1996 

PLACE: THE McLEOD LAW FIRM 

 

