A. Yes. Until -- until the following -- no. I didn't know until the 

following morning. 

 

Q. Then what happened? 

 

A. well, it sort of -- I think it was on the news or something like that. I 

am not sure. 

 

Q. Did you see Mr. Simpson the following morning? 

 

A. No, I did not. 

 

