conversation? 

 

A. Yes, I think so. 

 

Q. Do you know where she was? 

 

A. No, I don't. 

 

Q. Do you know what year this conversation occurred in? 

 

A. No, I don't. 

 

Q. Do you know what month it occurred in? 

 

A. No, I don't, sir. 

 

Q. Do you know where you were when you made the phone call? 

 

A. No , I don't. 

 

