statement? 

 

A. She didn't want to talk about it. 

 

Q. She refused to talk about it? 

 

A. Yes.  

 

Q. Did you talk about anything else in that conversation? 

 

A. No. 

 

Q. Did you ever speak with any of Nicole's friends about the statement 

that she made to Mr. Simpson about your alleged relationship? 

 

A. No, I did not. 

 

Q. Did you make any other efforts to talk to Nicole about this statement 

