Q: What did you do, just go to summer ball with them? 
 
A: No. As a matter of fact, I played a league game with them, the 
first game of the year, and I didn't like Seattle, so I asked for my 
release. 
 
Q: And they gave it to you? 
 
A: Yes.    
 
