key to open the gate. 
 
Q: And then you manually opened the gate? 
 
A: Automatically.  When you put the key and turn it, it 
automatically opens. 
 
Q: Does it disengage, or does it open all the way by itself? 
 
A: By itself? No. You have to turn this key to open the gate. It 
stays open for a few seconds. Once it's completely open, then it 
closes automatically. 
 
Q: Okay. Do you recall whether you parked in the driveway or on 
