BY MR. KELLY: 
 
Q: Mr. Cowlings, you played high school football? 
 
A: Yes, I did. 
 
Q: College football? 
 
A: Yes, I did. 
 
Q: Pro football? 
 
A: Yes, I did. 
 
Q: Seen a lot of injuries in your day?  
 
A: Yes, I have. 
 
