A: I never watched Ron Shipp play tennis, so I don't know what he 
did after that. 
 
Q: Okay.  But you saw him there on a regular basis? 
 
MR. LEONARD: Objection. "Regular basis."  Vague. 
 
THE WITNESS: He was there.  I don't know how regular it was, 
