A: No, sir. 
 
Q: Did anybody caution you to watch your step in any way? 
 
A: No, sir. 
 
Q: Okay.  Was Mr. Kaelin still on the premises when you left with 
the kids? 
 
A: I remember seeing Kato getting into the black-and-white. 
 
Q: Okay.  Do you remember seeing him actually exit the residence 
