A: I think Vannatter got on the phone for a few seconds. 
 
Q: Okay. First of all, could you tell me what your phone 
conversation was with Fuhrman when you called back up to 
Rockingham, 
 
A: That we had arrived in Laguna. 
 
Q: Did you tell him anything else? 
 
A: No. 
 
Q: Did he ask you anything else? 
 
A: Not that I remember. 
 
Q: Okay.  And what, if anything, did you discuss with Vannatter 
