"How's she doing?"  And he said -- I guess he said, "She's all 
right," or whatever. Then he put her on the phone. 
 
Q: And was that in the morning of June 13th? 
 
A: I don't now if it was the morning, late morning or early 
afternoon.  I don't know exactly when. 
 
Q: Do you know how long after you had arrived down at the 
