we -- it became a standard thing during the off-season that we'd play softball 
games on the weekends, and we had -- the Daisy had put together a team. Jack -- 
what was his name? He's passed away. He was the owner of The Daisy --  
 
MR. PETROCELLI: Hanson? 
 
THE WITNESS: Hanson, right. Jack Hanson put together -- he was very athletic 
