A: I don't recall.  I really don't recall. 
 
Q: Was it within a month of Nicole's death? 
 
A: I think it was later than that.  I think it was after my motorcycle 
trip to South Dakota, which is always in the first week of August.  I 
believe it was after that. 
 
MR. RUBALCAVA: It would have been after August 5th. 
 
THE WITNESS: Yeah, probably after August 15th. 
 
BY MR. PETROCELLI: 
 
