A: Well, I think in those days still Kris, Bruce, Paul, everybody 
thought that that's -- that was what happened. 
 
Q: But there was no information to support that. True? 
 
A: No. 
 
Q: True? 
 
A: Yeah. 
 
Q: Before the break I was asking you some questions about contacts 
