A: Nicole-free-basing, no.  Nicole admitted in the intervention that 
she had used cocaine with Faye at a couple opportunities, couple 
times. 
 
Q: But no free-basing. 
 
A: No free-basing.  And the word ''free-basing'' wasn't specifically 
used. 
 
Q: Now, at the intervention did it come up that Faye had been free-
basing? 
 
A: Yeah. 
 
Q: And the purpose of the intervention was to intervene in Faye's life 
and try to get her some help.  Right? 
 
A: Yeah. 
 
Q: And in that vein, she was confronted by you and her friends, 
