A: That's correct. 
 
Q: And who else? 
 
A: Faye. 
 
Q: And anyone else? 
 
A: The kids. 
 
Q: Francesca? 
 
A: Francesca. 
 
Q: And the [Name Deleted] children? 
 
A: And the [Name Deleted] children.  And one of  the [Name 
Deleted] daughter's is called Nicole, her boyfriend. 
 
Q: Anyone else? 
 
A: No.  That was it. 
 
Q: So your relationship with Faye had not obviously ended by this 
