A: No. 
 
Q -- or would make things up against O.J. Simpson? 
 
A: No. 
 
MR. LEONARD: Objection. 
 
BY MR. PETROCELLI: 
 
Q: Have you ever discussed with Mr. Simpson his belief as 
testified to in his deposition that  Nicole invented all of these 
