A: No. 
 
Q: Pointing out where things were found? 
 
A: No. 
 
Q: Do you know, for example, as you sit here today why blood 
drops were found on his property? 
 
A: I have from pictures and photographs that I have seen, but no. 
 
Q: You have seen photographs? 
 
A: Yes.  Whatever pops up on television sometimes. 
 
Q: Has Mr. Simpson ever said anything about the location of those 
blood drops found on his property? 
 
A: No. 
 
Q: No discussion at all? 
 
A: No. 
 
Q: No discussions at all relative to the glove, where it was found? 
 
A: No.  I don't think so. 
 
Q: Or the fact that there was no blood around the glove where, 
