A: No. No. 
 
Q: What were the things that you told her were untrue? 
 
A: The way she was portraying the -- particularly the two incidents 
at the sushi bar and -- 
 
Q: And Toscana? 
 
A: And Toscana. 
 
Q: And in both of those portrayals you thought her portrayal of 
