A: No. 
 
Q: Wasn't he asking you to set the record straight as far as Faye 
Resnick was concerned? 
 
A: No. 
 
Q: And to go public and refute Faye's story? 
 
A: He had asked me on one occasion that if I found something 
wrong in Faye's first book, whether I would comment. 
 
Q: You mean to say that if you find something wrong rather than 
you know something's wrong? 
 
A: Right. 
 
Q: Why would he say "if" if you and he knew for a fact that Faye's 
